mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:11px;--mit-font-weight:800;--mit-line-height:1em;--mit-text-color:#FFFFFF'>Отправить</p></div></div><svg class="mit-Me9wI mit-1ohuo7u" role="presentation" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#3028356511"></use></svg></div></div><div class="mit-1hkxw8m" data-border="true" data-mit-name="Launch Step Auto"><div class="mit-90f1si" data-mit-name="Step Header"><div class="mit-mm6poi"><svg class="mit-t9b6j mit-8rfihh" role="presentation" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#3408069395"></use></svg></div></div><div class="mit-j62ned" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtODAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:20px;--mit-font-weight:800;--mit-line-height:1.1em;--mit-text-color:rgb(26, 31, 43)'>Ассистент создаётся и запускается</p></div><div class="mit-1syldkv" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtcmVndWxhcg==;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-line-height:1.35em;--mit-text-color:rgb(94, 107, 127)'>После отправки формы агент начинает установку без созвонов и долгого внедрения.</p></div><div class="mit-1495n5o" data-mit-name="Auto Setup Visual"><div class="mit-14sgsv5"></div><div class="mit-9dbigg"></div></div></div><div class="mit-1sv1a6q" data-border="true" data-mit-name="Launch Step Telegram"><div class="mit-12u0fgw" data-mit-name="Step Header"><div class="mit-lp3azd"><div class="mit-6yIxv mit-18guuoc"></div></div></div><div class="mit-1ql8lfi" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtODAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:20px;--mit-font-weight:800;--mit-line-height:1.1em;--mit-text-color:rgb(26, 31, 43)'>Получаете МИТ ассистента в Telegram</p></div><div class="mit-ww2zuo" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtcmVndWxhcg==;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-line-height:1.35em;--mit-text-color:rgb(94, 107, 127)'>Ассистент появляется в вашем рабочем контуре и готов принимать задачи.</p></div><div class="mit-19l763f" data-mit-name="Telegram Appears Visual"><div class="mit-6yIxv mit-7e1k6f"></div><div class="mit-cg4vqr" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtODAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:12px;--mit-font-weight:800;--mit-line-height:1em;--mit-text-color:#1685C7'>МИТ онлайн</p></div></div></div><div class="mit-9nxrd9" data-border="true" data-mit-name="Launch Step Work"><div class="mit-jgml3a" data-mit-name="Step Header"><div class="mit-zv94jq"><svg class="mit-1xClZ mit-nrwcbf" role="presentation" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#1114939546"></use></svg></div></div><div class="mit-1yit82u" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtODAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:20px;--mit-font-weight:800;--mit-line-height:1.1em;--mit-text-color:rgb(26, 31, 43)'>Развиваете под свой контекст</p></div><div class="mit-1kii9y2" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtcmVndWxhcg==;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-line-height:1.35em;--mit-text-color:rgb(94, 107, 127)'>Добавляете навыки, интеграции и правила работы под свои процессы.</p></div><div class="mit-1vpp0vq" data-mit-name="Work Started Visual"><svg class="mit-zoKyS mit-12mpcb3" role="presentation" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#3843465606"></use></svg><div class="mit-wu6ibb" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtODAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:12px;--mit-font-weight:800;--mit-line-height:1em;--mit-text-color:#0D6B6B'>контур работает</p></div></div></div></div><div class="mit-m78cnt" data-mit-name="Vertical Route"></div><div class="mit-1u59ixy" data-border="true" data-mit-name="Speed Note"><svg class="mit-p8Aay mit-p7oqkt" role="presentation" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#4166249800"></use></svg><div class="mit-fd3xq2" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtNzAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-font-weight:700;--mit-line-height:1.25em;--mit-text-color:#1685C7'>Базовый запуск — около 30 минут после заявки.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="mit-z4ncfl" data-mit-name="Pricing" id="pricing"><div class="mit-1n8zsbq" data-border="true" data-mit-name="Single Pricing Offer"><div class="mit-rxaf6x" data-mit-name="Price Copy"><div class="mit-1m79ix6" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtNzAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:14px;--mit-font-weight:700;--mit-line-height:1em;--mit-text-color:#0D6B6B'>Один тариф для всех</p></div><div class="mit-mh4h91" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtODAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:58px;--mit-font-weight:800;--mit-letter-spacing:-0.04em;--mit-line-height:1em;--mit-text-color:rgb(26, 31, 43)'>10 000 ₽ / мес</p></div><div class="mit-1gittr0" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtcmVndWxhcg==;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:17px;--mit-line-height:1.45em;--mit-text-color:#5E6B7F'>Готовый МИТ ассистент в Telegram с запуском, поддержкой, сервером и базовыми навыками.</p></div></div><div class="mit-1dlmcvr" data-border="true" data-mit-name="Included"><div class="mit-rndt5k" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtODAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:20px;--mit-font-weight:800;--mit-line-height:1.1em;--mit-text-color:rgb(26, 31, 43)'>Что входит</p></div><div class="mit-wvjyg7" data-mit-name="Included Items"><div class="mit-12ldybf" data-mit-name="Included Item"><svg class="mit-1xClZ mit-rmsr74" role="presentation" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#1114939546"></use></svg><div class="mit-1p9zdii" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtNjAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-font-weight:600;--mit-text-color:#1A1F2B'>Запуск за 30 минут</p></div></div><div class="mit-1pkleq7" data-mit-name="Included Item"><svg class="mit-AUvx7 mit-or8oel" role="presentation" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#3684946077"></use></svg><div class="mit-14qx1i" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtNjAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-font-weight:600;--mit-text-color:#1A1F2B'>Отдельный сервер</p></div></div><div class="mit-12v4sf0" data-mit-name="Included Item"><svg class="mit-gtpAO mit-13nfqth" role="presentation" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#425173927"></use></svg><div class="mit-114u422" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtNjAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-font-weight:600;--mit-text-color:#1A1F2B'>AI-модели</p></div></div><div class="mit-1k88g17" data-mit-name="Included Item"><svg class="mit-iDVkO mit-byho17" role="presentation" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#332324033"></use></svg><div class="mit-9p7q16" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtNjAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-font-weight:600;--mit-text-color:#1A1F2B'>Поддержка 24/7</p></div></div><div class="mit-18wzl56" data-mit-name="Included Item"><svg class="mit-aZbuY mit-14bxtqx" role="presentation" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#3651586927"></use></svg><div class="mit-g5l69a" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtNjAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-font-weight:600;--mit-text-color:#1A1F2B'>Улучшение под контекст</p></div></div><div class="mit-3ukroy" data-mit-name="Included Item"><svg class="mit-p1X33 mit-xrl6m7" role="presentation" viewbox="0 0 24 24"><use href="#4191764975"></use></svg><div class="mit-fhag3v" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtNjAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-font-weight:600;--mit-text-color:#1A1F2B'>Базовые навыки</p></div></div></div><a class="mit-awnloa mit-lux5qc" data-mit-name="Price CTA" href="./#lead-form"><div class="mit-jfo2eh" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtODAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:15px;--mit-font-weight:800;--mit-line-height:1em;--mit-text-color:#FFFFFF'>Запустить МИТ Ассистент</p></div></a></div></div></section><section class="mit-fy3r39" data-mit-name="FAQ and Lead Form" id="faq"><div class="mit-vk5liw" data-mit-name="FAQ"><div class="mit-2ej1eb" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><h2 class="mit-text text-preset-aqyig4" dir="auto">FAQ</h2></div><div class="mit-1eo<div class="mit-1eowo8l" data-mit-name="FAQ Grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:18px;width:100%;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;">
      <div class="mit-faq-item" data-mit-name="FAQ Item" style="position:relative;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-radius:16px;cursor:pointer;transition:box-shadow .2s ease;overflow:visible;z-index:1;">
        <div class="mit-faq-row" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:22px 26px;">
          <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1F2B;line-height:1.35em;">Сколько занимает настройка?</p>
          <span class="mit-faq-plus" style="flex-shrink:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#2AABEE;line-height:1;transition:transform .3s ease;">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mit-faq-answer" style="position:absolute;left:0;right:0;top:100%;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;opacity:0;padding:0 26px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-top:none;border-radius:0 0 16px 16px;z-index:20;transform:none;transition:max-height .35s ease,opacity .35s ease,padding .35s ease;box-shadow:0 12px 24px rgba(26,31,43,.08);">
          <p style="margin:0;padding:12px 0 22px;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.55em;color:#5E6B7F;">От 1 до 3 дней после заявки. Мы настраиваем сервер, базовые навыки и интеграции под ваш контекст.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mit-faq-item" data-mit-name="FAQ Item" style="position:relative;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-radius:16px;cursor:pointer;transition:box-shadow .2s ease;overflow:visible;z-index:1;">
        <div class="mit-faq-row" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:22px 26px;">
          <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1F2B;line-height:1.35em;">Можно ли развивать ассистента?</p>
          <span class="mit-faq-plus" style="flex-shrink:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#2AABEE;line-height:1;transition:transform .3s ease;">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mit-faq-answer" style="position:absolute;left:0;right:0;top:100%;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;opacity:0;padding:0 26px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-top:none;border-radius:0 0 16px 16px;z-index:20;transform:none;transition:max-height .35s ease,opacity .35s ease,padding .35s ease;box-shadow:0 12px 24px rgba(26,31,43,.08);">
          <p style="margin:0;padding:12px 0 22px;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.55em;color:#5E6B7F;">Да. МИТ умеет учиться на ваших задачах — вы показываете процесс один раз, ассистент запоминает шаги и повторяет их сам.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mit-faq-item" data-mit-name="FAQ Item" style="position:relative;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-radius:16px;cursor:pointer;transition:box-shadow .2s ease;overflow:visible;z-index:1;">
        <div class="mit-faq-row" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:22px 26px;">
          <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1F2B;line-height:1.35em;">Безопасны ли мои данные?</p>
          <span class="mit-faq-plus" style="flex-shrink:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#2AABEE;line-height:1;transition:transform .3s ease;">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mit-faq-answer" style="position:absolute;left:0;right:0;top:100%;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;opacity:0;padding:0 26px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-top:none;border-radius:0 0 16px 16px;z-index:20;transform:none;transition:max-height .35s ease,opacity .35s ease,padding .35s ease;box-shadow:0 12px 24px rgba(26,31,43,.08);">
          <p style="margin:0;padding:12px 0 22px;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.55em;color:#5E6B7F;">Да. Все данные хранятся на вашем изолированном сервере. Доступ есть только у вас, ничего не передаётся третьим лицам.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mit-faq-item" data-mit-name="FAQ Item" style="position:relative;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-radius:16px;cursor:pointer;transition:box-shadow .2s ease;overflow:visible;z-index:1;">
        <div class="mit-faq-row" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:22px 26px;">
          <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1F2B;line-height:1.35em;">Какие навыки уже есть внутри?</p>
          <span class="mit-faq-plus" style="flex-shrink:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#2AABEE;line-height:1;transition:transform .3s ease;">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mit-faq-answer" style="position:absolute;left:0;right:0;top:100%;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;opacity:0;padding:0 26px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-top:none;border-radius:0 0 16px 16px;z-index:20;transform:none;transition:max-height .35s ease,opacity .35s ease,padding .35s ease;box-shadow:0 12px 24px rgba(26,31,43,.08);">
          <p style="margin:0;padding:12px 0 22px;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.55em;color:#5E6B7F;">Базовые навыки: задачи, календарь, документы, отчёты, напоминания. Любой другой навык мы собираем под ваш процесс.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mit-faq-item" data-mit-name="FAQ Item" style="position:relative;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-radius:16px;cursor:pointer;transition:box-shadow .2s ease;overflow:visible;z-index:1;">
        <div class="mit-faq-row" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:22px 26px;">
          <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1F2B;line-height:1.35em;">Что такое свой навык?</p>
          <span class="mit-faq-plus" style="flex-shrink:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#2AABEE;line-height:1;transition:transform .3s ease;">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mit-faq-answer" style="position:absolute;left:0;right:0;top:100%;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;opacity:0;padding:0 26px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-top:none;border-radius:0 0 16px 16px;z-index:20;transform:none;transition:max-height .35s ease,opacity .35s ease,padding .35s ease;box-shadow:0 12px 24px rgba(26,31,43,.08);">
          <p style="margin:0;padding:12px 0 22px;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.55em;color:#5E6B7F;">Это автоматизация вашей повторяющейся работы. Вы объясняете ассистенту алгоритм один раз — он выполняет её сам по команде.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mit-faq-item" data-mit-name="FAQ Item" style="position:relative;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-radius:16px;cursor:pointer;transition:box-shadow .2s ease;overflow:visible;z-index:1;">
        <div class="mit-faq-row" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:22px 26px;">
          <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1F2B;line-height:1.35em;">Что входит в стоимость?</p>
          <span class="mit-faq-plus" style="flex-shrink:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#2AABEE;line-height:1;transition:transform .3s ease;">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mit-faq-answer" style="position:absolute;left:0;right:0;top:100%;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;opacity:0;padding:0 26px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-top:none;border-radius:0 0 16px 16px;z-index:20;transform:none;transition:max-height .35s ease,opacity .35s ease,padding .35s ease;box-shadow:0 12px 24px rgba(26,31,43,.08);">
          <p style="margin:0;padding:12px 0 22px;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.55em;color:#5E6B7F;">Сервер, настройка ассистента, базовые навыки, интеграции и поддержка. В 14-дневном пробном периоде — полный функционал без ограничений.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mit-faq-item" data-mit-name="FAQ Item" style="position:relative;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-radius:16px;cursor:pointer;transition:box-shadow .2s ease;overflow:visible;z-index:1;">
        <div class="mit-faq-row" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:22px 26px;">
          <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1F2B;line-height:1.35em;">Чем МИТ отличается от ChatGPT?</p>
          <span class="mit-faq-plus" style="flex-shrink:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#2AABEE;line-height:1;transition:transform .3s ease;">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mit-faq-answer" style="position:absolute;left:0;right:0;top:100%;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;opacity:0;padding:0 26px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-top:none;border-radius:0 0 16px 16px;z-index:20;transform:none;transition:max-height .35s ease,opacity .35s ease,padding .35s ease;box-shadow:0 12px 24px rgba(26,31,43,.08);">
          <p style="margin:0;padding:12px 0 22px;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.55em;color:#5E6B7F;">МИТ работает в Telegram, запоминает ваш контекст, имеет доступ к вашим документам и календарю, действует от вашего имени.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mit-faq-item" data-mit-name="FAQ Item" style="position:relative;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-radius:16px;cursor:pointer;transition:box-shadow .2s ease;overflow:visible;z-index:1;">
        <div class="mit-faq-row" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:22px 26px;">
          <p style="margin:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1F2B;line-height:1.35em;">Можно ли интегрировать свои сервисы?</p>
          <span class="mit-faq-plus" style="flex-shrink:0;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#2AABEE;line-height:1;transition:transform .3s ease;">+</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mit-faq-answer" style="position:absolute;left:0;right:0;top:100%;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;opacity:0;padding:0 26px;background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7eaf0;border-top:none;border-radius:0 0 16px 16px;z-index:20;transform:none;transition:max-height .35s ease,opacity .35s ease,padding .35s ease;box-shadow:0 12px 24px rgba(26,31,43,.08);">
          <p style="margin:0;padding:12px 0 22px;font-family:'Geist',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.55em;color:#5E6B7F;">Да. Telegram, почта, календарь, базы знания, API и внутренние системы — подключаем под ваши задачи.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
</div></div><div class="mit-1s3dbzb" data-border="true" data-mit-name="Lead Form Card" id="lead-form"><div class="mit-ve1gsr" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtODAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:30px;--mit-font-weight:800;--mit-line-height:1.08em;--mit-text-color:#1A1F2B'>Оставьте заявку — и МИТ начнёт установку</p></div><div class="mit-ijgy04" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtcmVndWxhcg==;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:15px;--mit-line-height:1.5em;--mit-text-color:#5E6B7F'>После отправки формы запуск ассистента начнётся автоматически. Без созвонов, ожидания менеджера и ручного согласования.</p></div><form class="mit-1waxqkd" data-mit-name="Application Form"><label class="mit-xla7nn"><div class="mit-1ig3cjj" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtNjAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-font-weight:600;--mit-line-height:1em;--mit-text-color:#1A1F2B'>Фамилия <span style="color:#dc2626">*</span></p></div><div class="mit-form-text-input mit-form-input-wrapper mit-1apms6n mit-form-text-input-type"><input class="mit-form-input mit-form-input-empty" name="last_name" placeholder="Иванов" required="" type="text" value="" pattern="[A-Za-zА-Яа-яЁё\- ]{2,}" minlength="2" title="Только буквы, дефис и пробел, минимум 2 символа"/></div></label><label class="mit-1imb7fo"><div class="mit-1wvewf4" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtNjAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-font-weight:600;--mit-line-height:1em;--mit-text-color:#1A1F2B'>Имя <span style="color:#dc2626">*</span></p></div><div class="mit-form-text-input mit-form-input-wrapper mit-1iunhxd mit-form-text-input-type"><input class="mit-form-input mit-form-input-empty" name="first_name" placeholder="Алексей" required="" type="text" value="" pattern="[A-Za-zА-Яа-яЁё\- ]{2,}" minlength="2" title="Только буквы, дефис и пробел, минимум 2 символа"/></div></label><label class="mit-1lzatob"><div class="mit-8fnkt6" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtNjAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-font-weight:600;--mit-line-height:1em;--mit-text-color:#1A1F2B'>Telegram <span style="color:#dc2626">*</span></p></div><div class="mit-form-text-input mit-form-input-wrapper mit-xvwmm6 mit-form-text-input-type"><input class="mit-form-input mit-form-input-empty" name="telegram" placeholder="@username" required="" type="text" value="" pattern="@?[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]{4,31}" minlength="5" title="Формат: @username (латиница, цифры, подчёркивание, от 5 символов)"/></div></label><label class="mit-1lzatob" style="display:flex!important;flex-flow:column!important;gap:7px!important;width:100%!important;position:relative!important"><div class="mit-8fnkt6" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none;position:relative!important"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtNjAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-font-weight:600;--mit-line-height:1em;--mit-text-color:#1A1F2B'>Почта <span style="color:#dc2626">*</span></p></div><div class="mit-form-text-input mit-form-input-wrapper mit-xvwmm6 mit-form-text-input-type" style="position:relative!important"><input class="mit-form-input mit-form-input-empty" name="email" placeholder="mail@example.com" required="" type="email" value=""/></div></label><label class="mit-pwr4d1"><div class="mit-wlkvmh" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtNjAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:13px;--mit-font-weight:600;--mit-line-height:1.25em;--mit-text-color:#1A1F2B'>Какую задачу хотите решать через ассистента?</p></div><div class="mit-form-text-input mit-form-input-wrapper mit-1qwfgjf mit-form-textarea-input-type"><textarea class="mit-form-input" name="task" placeholder="Например: собирать отчёты, разбирать входящие, готовить документы…" minlength="10" title="Минимум 10 символов"></textarea></div></label><div class="mit-1y53hpc-container"><button class="mit-p4cOq mit-1e9qc37 mit-v-1e9qc37" data-mit-name="Default" data-reset="button" style="background-color:rgb(42, 171, 238);width:100%;border-bottom-left-radius:16px;border-bottom-right-radius:16px;border-top-left-radius:16px;border-top-right-radius:16px" type="submit"><div class="mit-3znzqm" data-mit-component-type="RichTextContainer" style="--extracted-r6o4lv:#FFFFFF;transform:none"><p class="mit-text" dir="auto" style='--font-selector:R0Y7R2Vpc3QtODAw;--mit-font-family:"Geist", "Geist Placeholder", sans-serif;--mit-font-size:15px;--mit-font-weight:800;--mit-line-height:1em;--mit-text-color:var(--extracted-r6o4lv, #FFFFFF)'>Запустить МИТ ассистента</p></div></button></div><input aria-hidden="true" autocomplete="one-time-code" data-1p-ignore="true" data-bwignore="true" data-form-type="other" data-lpignore="true" name="website" style="position:absolute;transform:scale(0)" tabindex="-1" type="text" value=""/><input aria-hidden="true" autocomplete="one-time-code" data-1p-ignore="true" data-bwignore="true" data-form-type="other" data-lpignore="true" name="company" style="position:absolute;transform:scale(0)" tabindex="-1" type="text" value=""/><input aria-hidden="true" autocomplete="one-time-code" data-1p-ignore="true" data-bwignore="true" data-form-type="other" data-lpig